long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
🚀 Effortlessly export Zillow search listing data.

🔧 How it Works:
1️⃣ Open an Zillow search listing page.
2️⃣ Click open our extension, then click the Export button.
3️⃣ Done! Sit back and just wait a moment, let our extension handle the rest.

🔥 Key Features:
1️⃣ Run in the background without waiting for finish.
2️⃣ Export on multiple product pages simultaneous.
3️⃣ Export listing data for current item to Excel or csv file, data include:  Zillow Property Id, Listing Status, Time On Zillow(days), Price, Property Area, Zestimate, Rent Zestimate, Lot Area, Bedroom And Bathroom Count, Address, Street, City, State, Zipcode, Geolocation, Broker Name, Is Zillow Owned, Image URL, Property Detail URL, Origin Search URL etcs.

🎯 Targeted Users: business owners, data analysts, and competitor researchers alike.

💡 Benefit from our dedicated support team! We're here to assist you at every step and provide prompt, knowledgeable help.

💪 Take control of your business data management and make informed decisions with Zillow Data Exporter today!

Note: This extension is an independent creation and is not affiliated with or endorsed by Zillow ❗️🔒
